org.grouplens.lenskit.eval.metrics

Annotation Type ResultColumn


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={METHOD,FIELD})
public @interface ResultColumn
    Specify the information for a column method in a metric response type.
    Since:
    2.1

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String value
      The name of this column.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      int order
      The order of this column.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract java.lang.String value
        The name of this column.
        Returns:
        The column name to use.

      • order

        public abstract int order
        The order of this column. A negative order indicates no preference. All unordered columns come after all ordered columns.
        Returns:
        The column order.
        Default:
        -1
